DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates initializing Parse Server with push notification support for both Android (FCM) and iOS (APNS) using a JavaScript configuration object. Dependencies include the ParseServer npm package and valid platform credentials (PFX/.p12 for iOS and API key for Android). Parameters under 'push' specify paths to credential files and relevant settings for each platform. The server is set up with database URI, cloud function path, app ID, and master key. The configuration supports sending notifications to both Android and Apple devices.
