TITLE: Periodic Config Refresh Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Implements a configuration refresh mechanism that fetches new config values at most once every 12 hours per app runtime.
SOURCE: https://github.com/parse-community/docs/blob/gh-pages/_includes/js/config.md#2025-04-22_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
// Fetches the config at most once every 12 hours per app runtime
const refreshConfig = function() {
  let lastFetchedDate;
  const configRefreshInterval = 12 * 60 * 60 * 1000;
  return function() {
    const currentDate = new Date();
    if (lastFetchedDate === undefined ||
        currentDate.getTime() - lastFetchedDate.getTime() > configRefreshInterval) {
      Parse.Config.get();
      lastFetchedDate = currentDate;
    }
  };
}();
```

