SOURCE: https://github.com/parse-community/docs/blob/gh-pages/_includes/rest/queries.md#2025-04-22_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
curl -X GET \
  -H "X-Parse-Application-Id: ${APPLICATION_ID}" \
  -H "X-Parse-REST-API-Key: ${REST_API_KEY}" \
  -G \
  --data-urlencode 'where={"score":{"$in":[1,3,5,7,9]}}' \
