TITLE: Custom Parse Object Class Definition
DESCRIPTION: Creates a custom Parse Object class with typed properties and clone functionality.
SOURCE: https://github.com/parse-community/docs/blob/gh-pages/_includes/dart/objects.md#2025-04-22_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: dart
CODE:
```
class DietPlan extends ParseObject implements ParseCloneable {

  DietPlan() : super(_keyTableName);
  DietPlan.clone(): this();

  /// Mimic a clone due to Flutter not using reflection
  @override clone(Map map) => DietPlan.clone()..fromJson(map);

  static const String _keyTableName = 'Diet_Plans';
  static const String keyName = 'Name';

  String get name => get<String>(keyName);
  set name(String name) => set<String>(keyName, name);
}
```

