TITLE: Checking Key Existence with whereKeyExists and whereKeyDoesNotExist in Parse Objective-C
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates filtering Parse objects based on whether a field is present or not using whereKeyExists and whereKeyDoesNotExist. NSPredicate alternatives using IN SELF and NOT (IN SELF) are also provided. Input is a field name, and results include/exclude objects based on existence.
SOURCE: https://github.com/parse-community/docs/blob/gh-pages/_includes/ios/queries.md#2025-04-22_snippet_26

LANGUAGE: objective_c
CODE:
```
// Finds objects that have the score set
