TITLE: Removing File Encryption in Parse Server using JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This JavaScript example describes removing encryption from files in Parse Server by stopping the use of an encryption key on the file adapter. It requires the `oldKey` to successfully decrypt existing encrypted files.
